SCOPE NOTE

The MIT license above covers the *code* in this repository (harness, judge,
analysis and build scripts).

It does NOT cover:

  * Text corpora under `corpora/`. Those are assembled from works in the public
    domain and from original text written for this study. Per-item attribution
    (`source`, `artist`, `passage`) is recorded in the corpus files themselves;
    reuse of public-domain material carries no restriction, but the attribution
    should travel with it.

  * Base model weights. None are redistributed here. Only trained adapters and
    their configs are published, and those remain subject to the license of the
    base model they adapt.
